WEBVTT

00:06.499 --> 00:07.840
(Respect copyright)

00:14.112 --> 00:20.704
♪Memories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreams♪

00:24.288 --> 00:30.432
♪Only by moving forward
can you find reunion♪

00:32.640 --> 00:35.872
♪Endings only mark new routes♪

00:36.096 --> 00:42.112
♪It's all part of the scenery♪

00:42.432 --> 00:45.856
♪To the horizon's call♪

00:45.920 --> 00:52.480
♪Your journey hasn't started♪

00:53.536 --> 00:57.472
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

00:57.472 --> 01:03.552
♪Let time embrace you
and wash away the past♪

01:03.840 --> 01:07.712
♪Put every twist behind you♪

01:07.712 --> 01:12.576
♪Drift leisurely through time♪

01:12.960 --> 01:15.680
♪Make headway against the wind♪

01:15.680 --> 01:18.667
♪Let mountains bow to your pace♪

01:18.720 --> 01:24.128
♪Rush towards a life without regret♪

01:24.640 --> 01:28.579
♪Let your nature burst free♪

01:30.240 --> 01:34.490
=The First Jasmine=

01:35.280 --> 01:37.808
=Episode 32=

01:38.690 --> 01:40.089
Even some spiced meat would do.

01:40.809 --> 01:42.690
This soup of yours is so watery.

01:42.690 --> 01:45.529
I can see my reflection in it.
How am I supposed to eat this?

01:46.010 --> 01:47.889
Any random street stall in the capital

01:47.889 --> 01:49.089
has spiced meat on hand.

01:50.369 --> 01:51.184
Sir, you jest.

01:51.470 --> 01:54.429
How can my little stall compare
to any shop in the capital?

01:54.670 --> 01:57.110
How about I add some more
chopped scallions for you?

01:59.429 --> 02:00.269
Please enjoy.

02:10.310 --> 02:11.109
Your Highness.

02:13.910 --> 02:16.389
You must be tired from the long journey.

02:16.509 --> 02:18.590
Not far ahead is Qingping County.

02:18.710 --> 02:20.270
It's getting late.

02:20.270 --> 02:21.669
Why don't we hurry on our way?

02:21.750 --> 02:23.710
We can stop in Qingping County

02:24.310 --> 02:26.270
and find a decent restaurant

02:26.270 --> 02:28.190
so Your Highness can have a hot meal.

02:28.190 --> 02:31.030
We can continue our journey
early tomorrow morning after resting up.

02:31.710 --> 02:33.310
No need. Are you done eating?

02:33.710 --> 02:34.590
Then let's go.

02:34.590 --> 02:35.190
I...

02:35.190 --> 02:35.829
Jin.

02:39.549 --> 02:42.310
Wait... well...

02:43.509 --> 02:45.470
Eunuch Shunxi, keep up.

02:48.349 --> 02:49.470
Alright, stop eating.

02:49.470 --> 02:50.349
Keep up now.

02:52.310 --> 02:53.150
Let's go.

03:14.829 --> 03:16.030
Hold to your posts.

03:16.150 --> 03:16.789
Yes.

03:17.190 --> 03:18.349
Please halt, honored guests.

03:18.800 --> 03:23.910
(Lishan Academy)

03:23.910 --> 03:27.069
Empress Dowager ordered Lishan Academy
closed for book compilation.

03:27.310 --> 03:29.310
No one shall ascend the mountain
and disturb them.

03:40.784 --> 03:41.470
(Decree)

03:41.470 --> 03:43.710
I am the chief eunuch of Anqing Palace.

03:43.710 --> 03:45.710
This is His Highness Prince Ding,

03:45.750 --> 03:48.048
the Lishan Pacification Commissioner
on imperial orders.

03:48.430 --> 03:49.629
Greetings, Your Highness.

03:51.710 --> 03:54.229
By order of Their Majesties,

03:54.229 --> 03:55.870
we bring imperial rewards

03:55.910 --> 03:58.109
to deliver imperial regards
to Lishan Academy.

03:58.389 --> 04:00.190
Open the gate immediately
to let us pass.

04:00.549 --> 04:02.590
Has the blockade of Lishan been lifted?

04:02.789 --> 04:03.629
Lifted?

04:04.069 --> 04:06.069
Blockade and pacification
are different matters.

04:09.549 --> 04:10.710
Her Majesty is benevolent.

04:10.750 --> 04:13.430
Considering the academy's
hard work in compiling books,

04:13.616 --> 04:14.672
she sent us here.

04:14.672 --> 04:16.390
It's the magnificent imperial grace.

04:17.869 --> 04:18.989
Can we go up now?

04:20.390 --> 04:21.989
Yes. Let them pass.

04:25.349 --> 04:26.309
- Your Highness.
- Your Highness.

04:28.176 --> 04:31.408
(Lishan Academy)

04:38.270 --> 04:39.669
Go away! Go away!

04:39.869 --> 04:40.669
Go!

04:40.950 --> 04:42.390
Why are you pecking only at me?

04:42.390 --> 04:42.950
Go!

04:43.950 --> 04:44.630
Scram!

04:47.408 --> 04:48.710
Alright, let's go.

05:22.192 --> 05:22.749
(Deep Contemplation)

05:22.749 --> 05:26.030
Imperial Pacification Commissioner
Prince Ding has come to pay a visit.

05:34.789 --> 05:36.590
Imperial Pacification Commissioner

05:37.150 --> 05:39.070
Prince Ding has come to pay a visit.

06:26.030 --> 06:27.669
You two, search over here.

06:27.669 --> 06:28.304
- Yes.
- Yes.

06:28.390 --> 06:29.789
You two, search over there.

06:29.789 --> 06:30.448
- Yes.
- Yes.

06:35.470 --> 06:36.830
Why are they running?

06:38.229 --> 06:39.030
Over here.

06:46.710 --> 06:47.510
Li?

07:09.669 --> 07:10.989
Why is there no one here at all?

07:15.830 --> 07:16.989
Li.

07:26.950 --> 07:28.109
Jin, let's split up.

07:28.910 --> 07:29.429
Yes.

07:31.390 --> 07:31.989
Keep up.

07:56.309 --> 07:57.070
Li.

08:00.549 --> 08:01.309
Li?

08:06.229 --> 08:06.950
Li?

08:13.510 --> 08:14.309
Li!

08:24.229 --> 08:26.189
Your Highness, Her Highness is inside.

08:37.968 --> 08:42.480
♪My life is full of ups and downs♪

08:44.144 --> 08:48.560
♪Every wound shows traces of love♪

08:51.789 --> 08:52.589
Li.

08:55.184 --> 08:57.936
♪Until you went over the hills♪

08:58.224 --> 09:00.880
♪To come close to me♪

09:02.192 --> 09:06.544
♪I saw your tender yet unwavering eyes♪

09:08.752 --> 09:12.848
♪Quietly full of joy and sorrow♪

09:13.648 --> 09:19.440
♪When it's over, I stand in the light♪

09:19.888 --> 09:24.400
♪In the reunion,
I comprehend the parting♪

09:26.669 --> 09:28.549
Why is your hair gray?

09:31.728 --> 09:37.776
♪As I travel through wind and frost,
I gaze at your figure♪

09:39.910 --> 09:40.789
I'm sorry.

09:45.069 --> 09:46.350
I'm sorry, Li.

09:55.309 --> 09:56.150
I'm sorry.

10:17.949 --> 10:19.949
By Her Majesty's decree,

10:20.150 --> 10:22.949
I'm with Prince Ding to offer
imperial regards to Lishan Academy.

10:23.469 --> 10:25.949
Your Highness, where are the people
of Lishan Academy?

10:26.110 --> 10:27.669
Where is Headmaster Xu?

10:27.750 --> 10:29.390
And where are all the masters?

10:29.510 --> 10:31.390
Why can't I see anyone in charge?

10:33.189 --> 10:34.669
They are not here.

10:35.949 --> 10:36.829
Not here?

10:39.030 --> 10:41.390
Lishan is sealed off. No one gets pass.

10:41.750 --> 10:44.469
If they're not at the academy,
where else could they be?

10:45.949 --> 10:46.750
They...

10:48.350 --> 10:50.789
They all went to the back mountain
to harvest rice.

10:52.189 --> 10:53.110
Harvesting rice?

10:54.549 --> 10:56.350
Headmaster Xu does such work himself?

10:57.110 --> 10:58.352
After the mountain was sealed,

10:58.789 --> 11:00.829
my grandfather led the academy

11:01.309 --> 11:03.429
to clear a field on the back mountain.

11:03.870 --> 11:06.949
They diverted water to grow rice
to feed us.

11:08.150 --> 11:10.469
Right now is the harvest season.

11:10.750 --> 11:12.230
So they are in that field.

11:16.669 --> 11:18.669
Then when will they return?

11:21.709 --> 11:24.189
Before sunset.
They'll be back before sunset.

11:24.910 --> 11:27.630
Very well, then I shall wait here.

11:29.829 --> 11:30.630
However,

11:31.949 --> 11:34.270
we've come a long way,
weary from the journey.

11:34.549 --> 11:35.949
We've hardly had food or water.

11:36.549 --> 11:39.750
Your Highness, does Lishan Academy
have any food?

11:41.230 --> 11:42.870
There's nothing ready-made.

11:43.750 --> 11:45.189
But the kitchen has rice and flour.

11:46.350 --> 11:47.789
And stove and firewood too.

11:48.189 --> 11:49.350
You may help yourselves.

11:54.429 --> 11:57.429
Then, Your Highness,
where is the kitchen?

12:05.949 --> 12:06.750
Alright.

12:25.150 --> 12:27.230
Senior Eunuch, I'll go check elsewhere.

12:28.110 --> 12:28.990
Go.

12:31.150 --> 12:31.949
Go inside and look.

12:31.952 --> 12:32.592
Yes.

12:46.110 --> 12:49.390
They're all leftover old supplies.
'Help yourselves,' she says.

12:50.110 --> 12:52.110
No decent firewood, food, or seasoning.

12:52.110 --> 12:53.150
How can we help ourselves?

12:54.150 --> 12:56.230
Senior Eunuch, look.

12:56.510 --> 12:57.630
There's some rice here.

13:00.309 --> 13:02.150
How are we supposed to eat this?

13:05.110 --> 13:07.669
Go look again.
See if there's anything to eat.

13:12.350 --> 13:13.429
Did you find anything?

13:15.150 --> 13:17.309
General, we didn't find anyone.

13:17.309 --> 13:18.750
Thick dust is everywhere.

13:18.750 --> 13:20.549
And moldy clothes and bedding.

13:23.990 --> 13:26.110
Senior Eunuch, I've looked around.

13:26.110 --> 13:27.189
Something's not right.

13:27.510 --> 13:28.350
What's not right?

13:28.789 --> 13:30.789
Although the academy
buildings still stand,

13:30.789 --> 13:31.990
thick dust is everywhere.

13:32.150 --> 13:34.789
The clothes and bedding
smell strongly of mildew,

13:34.789 --> 13:36.432
as if untouched for a long time.

13:36.949 --> 13:38.549
No one seems to live here.

13:42.589 --> 13:45.630
Are you saying they ran away long ago?

13:45.990 --> 13:47.230
I dare not presume.

13:47.589 --> 13:49.552
It's just that it does seem odd.

13:54.469 --> 13:55.990
Take men to the back mountain

13:55.990 --> 13:58.270
and see if anyone's in the rice field.

13:58.589 --> 13:59.390
Yes.

14:48.949 --> 14:49.949
You must be hungry.

14:50.829 --> 14:53.309
I picked this this morning. Eat up.

15:08.469 --> 15:09.270
Yao,

15:11.309 --> 15:12.789
what happened exactly?

15:14.110 --> 15:15.949
Why has your hair gone so gray?

15:20.870 --> 15:21.669
Li,

15:25.949 --> 15:28.789
those past grudges
have nothing to do with you.

15:30.709 --> 15:32.350
I shouldn't have taken it out on you.

15:34.350 --> 15:35.390
It's my fault.

15:38.390 --> 15:39.390
After you left,

15:43.069 --> 15:44.150
I missed you so much.

15:46.949 --> 15:48.350
Don't blame me anymore, alright?

15:50.949 --> 15:52.669
Come back to the mansion
with me, alright?

16:03.309 --> 16:05.549
Is that why your hair turned gray?

16:22.789 --> 16:24.390
Please wait a little longer.

16:24.510 --> 16:26.669
Whatever it is,
wait until His Highness comes out.

16:26.789 --> 16:28.309
I can't wait any longer.

16:28.350 --> 16:29.309
Eunuch Shunxi.

16:36.030 --> 16:36.910
Princess Ding,

16:38.549 --> 16:41.309
where exactly are the people
of Lishan Academy?

16:41.709 --> 16:43.189
Didn't I just say it?

16:43.669 --> 16:45.350
They are harvesting
on the back mountain.

16:45.829 --> 16:47.150
Why are you asking again?

16:47.230 --> 16:50.709
Please don't make a fool of me
as if I were a three-year-old child.

16:51.270 --> 16:52.949
The rice field you mentioned

16:53.150 --> 16:55.350
is overrun with vermin and weeds.

16:55.350 --> 16:57.189
It's clearly been abandoned for years.

16:57.230 --> 16:58.230
All over Lishan Mountain,

16:58.270 --> 17:01.030
there isn't even the slightest warmth
of human habitation.

17:01.030 --> 17:02.110
The entire Lishan Mountain

17:02.150 --> 17:04.509
has no one else except you,
Princess Ding.

17:08.110 --> 17:08.910
No one?

17:12.310 --> 17:13.390
So wonderful!

17:14.949 --> 17:18.429
Thank you for your guidance, Headmaster.
We will remember it well.

17:19.590 --> 17:21.269
Come on. Get up here.

17:22.960 --> 17:25.680
(Lishan Academy)

17:34.550 --> 17:35.429
No one is here?

17:35.749 --> 17:36.590
Li.

17:37.509 --> 17:38.749
By Her Majesty's decree,

17:38.910 --> 17:41.949
the whole of Lishan Academy
shall remain here to compile books.

17:42.029 --> 17:45.029
Fleeing in secret is open defiance
of the imperial decree.

17:45.269 --> 17:47.029
(Li, it's too dangerous here.)

17:47.390 --> 17:49.648
(Go now! Just go!)

17:49.648 --> 17:51.110
(Master Zhu, please let me in.)

17:51.110 --> 17:52.150
(I can take care of you.)

17:52.150 --> 17:53.110
(My lady.)

17:53.350 --> 17:56.350
How could there be no one?

17:57.630 --> 17:58.429
Li!

17:58.949 --> 17:59.749
Your Highness!

17:59.749 --> 18:00.790
I haven't finished yet.

18:01.029 --> 18:01.830
After them!

18:02.830 --> 18:04.029
Support me. After them!

18:05.110 --> 18:06.110
Hurry up!

18:08.310 --> 18:09.110
Li!

18:11.590 --> 18:12.509
Wait, you...

18:12.509 --> 18:13.749
You two, slow down!

18:13.749 --> 18:15.110
Wait, slow down.

18:16.390 --> 18:17.189
Li.

18:17.709 --> 18:18.509
Your Highness.

18:21.110 --> 18:21.630
Wait.

18:21.630 --> 18:22.630
Senior Eunuch, slow down.

18:26.790 --> 18:27.590
Li.

18:28.910 --> 18:29.749
No one is here.

18:32.550 --> 18:34.029
How could there be no one?

18:34.870 --> 18:36.070
Li, don't panic.

18:36.070 --> 18:38.189
Let's go back.
I'll explain it all slowly, alright?

18:38.669 --> 18:39.590
Don't panic yet.

18:41.910 --> 18:43.029
Of course there's no one.

18:44.790 --> 18:47.429
Princess Ding, you led us all the way
up the mountain path

18:47.749 --> 18:49.429
just to come to this rice field?

18:49.949 --> 18:51.110
Then I have a question.

18:52.029 --> 18:53.350
The rice field you mentioned

18:53.469 --> 18:55.310
was last farmed six or seven years ago.

18:55.310 --> 18:56.110
Shut up!

19:03.550 --> 19:05.509
Li, don't be like this.

19:05.509 --> 19:07.429
Li. Li.

19:09.110 --> 19:09.709
Li.

19:23.029 --> 19:26.070
Li? Li!

20:14.229 --> 20:14.989
Your Highness.

20:35.070 --> 20:38.590
Your Highness, Shunxi and his party
have left the mountain overnight,

20:38.910 --> 20:42.070
saying they'd return to the capital now
to report to the Empress Dowager.

20:43.189 --> 20:44.110
As I expected.

20:44.989 --> 20:46.189
You go down the mountain too.

20:46.949 --> 20:49.390
Deliver this letter
to His Majesty for me.

20:50.110 --> 20:52.630
What about you and Her Highness?

20:54.150 --> 20:55.390
I will stay here with her.

20:57.550 --> 20:58.350
Yes.

21:28.310 --> 21:29.110
Li?

21:31.229 --> 21:32.029
Li!

21:35.749 --> 21:36.550
Li.

21:38.310 --> 21:41.070
Li? Li?

21:49.150 --> 21:49.949
Li?

22:00.910 --> 22:01.709
Li.

22:16.429 --> 22:19.310
You're awake.
Did you sleep well last night?

22:33.310 --> 22:34.229
Where did you go?

22:34.989 --> 22:36.630
I went to dig for bamboo shoots.

22:37.229 --> 22:39.630
And I got lucky
and found some fresh mushrooms too.

22:40.029 --> 22:41.429
I'll make soup for you in a bit.

22:42.768 --> 22:46.960
♪You always love with pain♪

22:48.368 --> 22:53.744
♪Forgetting you deserve to be loved too♪

22:56.560 --> 23:02.160
♪How the rain outside
nurtures the heart♪

23:02.768 --> 23:07.152
♪That's how you are cherished♪

23:08.464 --> 23:11.984
♪You don't need to chase♪

23:11.984 --> 23:15.312
♪After clouds that winds pursue♪

23:15.408 --> 23:18.800
♪You can silently watch each sunrise♪

23:18.800 --> 23:21.744
♪Finding happiness by your side♪

23:22.320 --> 23:25.488
♪You don't need to chart a map♪

23:25.712 --> 23:28.720
♪Of every bend where love winds on♪

23:29.232 --> 23:32.400
♪Nor travel far to guide its course♪

23:32.528 --> 23:35.472
♪To make your heart♪

23:36.496 --> 23:39.440
♪Warm again♪

23:39.989 --> 23:41.110
Li, let me help you.

23:42.029 --> 23:43.110
Where are the bowls?

23:43.590 --> 23:44.269
Over there.

23:53.168 --> 23:57.296
♪Time has kept some lines alive♪

23:58.704 --> 24:04.336
♪They've recorded of your dreams♪

24:06.640 --> 24:12.560
♪How the snow on the peak
buries the wounds♪

24:13.488 --> 24:18.160
♪That's how you will be trusted♪

24:18.992 --> 24:22.256
♪You don't need to chase♪

24:22.256 --> 24:25.680
♪After clouds that winds pursue♪

24:25.904 --> 24:29.264
♪You can silently watch each sunrise♪

24:29.264 --> 24:32.560
♪Finding happiness by your side♪

24:32.560 --> 24:35.984
♪You don't need to chart a map♪

24:35.984 --> 24:39.376
♪Of every bend where love winds on♪

24:39.376 --> 24:42.704
♪Nor travel far to guide its course♪

24:43.229 --> 24:44.070
Drink up.

24:45.168 --> 24:48.432
♪Warm again♪

24:52.790 --> 24:54.469
Is the taste too bland?

24:54.910 --> 24:56.469
We're out of seasonings.

24:56.870 --> 24:58.310
Salt's nearly gone as well.

25:00.390 --> 25:02.830
There's a patch of ground
under the eastern cliff.

25:03.189 --> 25:05.989
Later, I'll go dig up
some salty earth from there

25:06.229 --> 25:07.749
and boil it down to get some salt.

25:08.550 --> 25:09.350
It's fine.

25:09.910 --> 25:11.989
The soup is savory and fresh.

25:13.709 --> 25:14.509
That's good.

25:21.269 --> 25:22.070
Yao,

25:23.830 --> 25:25.709
why is your hair gray?

25:28.870 --> 25:30.790
When did you arrive last night?

25:31.630 --> 25:34.189
After I fell asleep?

25:35.429 --> 25:37.429
Did something happen in the mansion?

25:44.189 --> 25:45.989
You don't remember
what happened yesterday?

25:47.269 --> 25:48.110
Yesterday?

25:49.989 --> 25:51.189
What happened yesterday?

26:07.630 --> 26:08.429
Yao?

26:15.029 --> 26:15.830
It's nothing.

26:17.229 --> 26:20.269
I arrived very late yesterday.
You were already asleep.

26:22.269 --> 26:23.590
Why didn't you wake me up?

26:26.070 --> 26:28.669
I was afraid you'd be angry
and send me off.

26:33.310 --> 26:35.189
How could I ever be angry with you?

26:55.310 --> 26:57.070
But I'm angry at myself.

27:08.429 --> 27:11.150
Right, Grandfather and the masters

27:11.189 --> 27:12.709
went to harvest rice in the back.

27:12.989 --> 27:15.390
They'll return later.
You'll see them then.

27:46.429 --> 27:48.070
Is there anything else to do today?

27:49.189 --> 27:51.229
Yes, there's serious business.

27:51.910 --> 27:52.790
Serious business?

28:04.749 --> 28:06.029
Indeed, serious business.

28:08.189 --> 28:10.070
Lishan's closure for book compilation

28:10.509 --> 28:12.029
is no mere for show.

28:12.790 --> 28:15.830
But the classics are vast,
and volumes pile like mountains.

28:16.989 --> 28:19.830
Compiling books is not a task
that can be done overnight.

28:22.070 --> 28:24.429
Grandfather and the masters
are getting older

28:24.709 --> 28:25.749
with declining energy.

28:26.669 --> 28:28.709
They can only offer
a little guidance each day.

28:31.870 --> 28:34.550
So the work of collation and compilation

28:35.229 --> 28:37.669
has fallen on the shoulders of me
and a few seniors.

28:42.350 --> 28:45.070
Unfortunately, my seniors
have been rather slack in recent years.

28:46.949 --> 28:47.728
(Compendium of Codes, Volume Six)
Look at this.

28:48.720 --> 28:50.288
In the days since I left the mountain,

28:50.429 --> 28:53.630
this volume of Compendium of Codes
hasn't made any progress at all.

28:55.469 --> 28:58.390
When the masters return, I'll definitely
have a word with them about it.

29:08.189 --> 29:08.989
I'll do it.

29:24.310 --> 29:25.229
What do you want?

29:25.550 --> 29:26.469
Treatise on Astronomy.

29:28.910 --> 29:30.350
Treatise on Astronomy?

29:33.910 --> 29:34.709
Here.

29:40.749 --> 29:43.830
Today I need to finish
the first draft collation

29:43.830 --> 29:45.749
of Astronomy Chapter
and Agriculture Chapter.

29:46.070 --> 29:47.550
It might take some time.

29:48.150 --> 29:50.590
If you're bored,
you can go out for a walk.

29:52.390 --> 29:53.429
I'll stay with you.

29:55.110 --> 29:55.910
Alright.

30:30.576 --> 30:35.920
♪Love is not just romance♪

30:36.560 --> 30:40.816
♪They don't get my obsession♪

30:43.350 --> 30:44.830
(Master Helai from Lishan)

30:44.870 --> 30:46.830
(is a renowned master physician.)

30:46.928 --> 30:48.790
(He wrote
Treatise on Injuries and Illnesses.)

30:48.790 --> 30:49.870
(Have you heard of it?)

30:51.110 --> 30:54.229
(I learned how to treat
bone injury from him.)

30:54.509 --> 30:56.830
(And I treated similar cases
up on the mountain.)

31:00.944 --> 31:04.272
♪To live once more for each other♪

31:05.008 --> 31:09.648
♪To become a better version
of ourselves♪

31:12.336 --> 31:16.592
♪The little and big things left
in each other's lives♪

31:17.168 --> 31:21.456
♪Along the way,
we've skipped the explanation of love♪

31:21.456 --> 31:24.080
♪Seeing a complete life♪

31:24.080 --> 31:29.296
♪Becoming mirrors for each other♪

31:32.469 --> 31:35.669
(Mo Xiuyao, let me treat your legs.)

31:37.029 --> 31:40.110
(I know you've sought treatment
many times before,)

31:40.749 --> 31:44.110
(seen many physicians,
and been through a lot.)

31:46.070 --> 31:49.509
But could you try one more time for me?

31:51.229 --> 31:53.070
I will definitely heal you.

31:53.264 --> 31:59.280
♪On such a long road,
I hold your fingers♪

32:05.229 --> 32:07.989
(Li, thank you.)

32:12.390 --> 32:13.189
Yao.

32:23.189 --> 32:26.310
Before I went up the mountain,
I promised your elder brother

32:26.709 --> 32:28.110
that I would heal your legs.

32:29.830 --> 32:32.870
But I didn't know
the extent of your leg injury.

32:33.189 --> 32:34.790
So I learned from Master Helai

32:35.350 --> 32:37.910
and carefully studied
bone injuries, paralysis,

32:38.070 --> 32:39.509
acupuncture and massage skills.

32:42.229 --> 32:44.350
I found this in an ancient text.

32:44.870 --> 32:46.949
I planned to make one for you
when seeing you.

32:47.590 --> 32:50.768
I didn't expect you'd already have one,
and it was better than mine.

32:56.630 --> 33:00.176
Yao, what's wrong?

33:03.590 --> 33:05.070
I feel like I'm really bad.

33:07.189 --> 33:08.550
Why do you say that?

33:09.550 --> 33:10.709
Thinking back carefully,

33:12.070 --> 33:14.469
I don't think
I've ever been good to you.

33:15.830 --> 33:18.150
At first, I suspected you,

33:18.749 --> 33:20.749
doubted you, and neglected you.

33:21.509 --> 33:25.390
Then I said I'd go with you
to the Ye Mansion, but I broke my word.

33:27.870 --> 33:29.669
And later, when you were in danger,

33:30.429 --> 33:31.870
I wasn't by your side.

33:33.709 --> 33:37.350
Don't say that. You've been good to me.

33:44.429 --> 33:45.550
Good or not,

33:47.110 --> 33:49.189
only the end
of our years together will tell.

34:33.149 --> 34:36.109
There are monkeys. So many.

34:36.949 --> 34:38.390
So many monkeys!

34:39.230 --> 34:42.310
Xiuyao said you saw monkeys
in the mansion?

34:45.949 --> 34:47.790
You must have been seeing things.

34:48.109 --> 34:49.710
The capital is heavily guarded,

34:49.830 --> 34:51.230
and the mansion has high walls.

34:51.670 --> 34:53.029
Monkeys wouldn't run rampant here.

34:53.830 --> 34:55.670
Jackdaws often perch on the rockery

34:55.830 --> 34:57.469
in the west corner of the backyard.

34:57.509 --> 35:00.190
Not jackdaws. Monkeys!

35:01.469 --> 35:03.429
I wasn't mistaken. There were monkeys!

35:37.230 --> 35:38.429
(Put your back into it!)

35:39.670 --> 35:43.029
No one carries goods on
a flatbed cart into the desert.

35:43.109 --> 35:44.589
I don't want it either.

35:45.069 --> 35:47.790
I ran into an unreliable guide.

35:48.270 --> 35:50.429
He robbed me of my horse
and took all my money.

35:51.230 --> 35:53.949
You'd rather go hungry every day
with this cart of treasures?

35:54.509 --> 35:55.989
Well, you don't know the whole story.

35:56.549 --> 35:59.109
This cart of goods is my dignity.

35:59.549 --> 36:01.310
No matter what,
I'll get it to the capital

36:01.350 --> 36:02.750
and present it before my father.

36:03.350 --> 36:05.949
You're nearly dead,
and you still talk about dignity?

36:06.192 --> 36:07.390
I'm hungry.

36:07.509 --> 36:08.469
Hungry again?

36:08.790 --> 36:10.469
I've picked up a glutton.

36:10.710 --> 36:13.509
I've been pushing this cart
the whole way. Of course, I'm hungry.

36:14.069 --> 36:16.509
Master, where are we going?

36:17.149 --> 36:18.310
What is this place?

36:20.432 --> 36:23.310
This is the road
Lingyun and I once walked.

36:44.270 --> 36:47.670
(Look, Lingyun,
that family is still here,)

36:48.230 --> 36:49.776
(living happily.)

37:00.790 --> 37:02.589
Master, where are you from?

37:03.310 --> 37:05.949
We're from the capital,
heading to Suixue Pass and then Cangbei.

37:06.864 --> 37:07.664
Come on in, please.

37:07.664 --> 37:08.589
Have some milk tea.

37:11.549 --> 37:12.350
Please sit.

37:13.830 --> 37:15.230
Pour the milk tea.

37:20.080 --> 37:22.672
So, Master, what are you
going to Cangbei for?

37:25.629 --> 37:26.429
To unwind.

37:26.670 --> 37:27.469
To unwind?

37:28.589 --> 37:31.949
That's good.
Cangbei and Dachu are now friends.

37:32.069 --> 37:34.230
The border markets are quite lively.

37:34.230 --> 37:38.029
Yes, this place looks much livelier
than it was two years ago.

37:38.230 --> 37:40.949
Now that there's no more war,
of course it's become lively.

37:40.949 --> 37:43.270
Everyone can make a living
with peace of mind.

37:43.270 --> 37:45.149
Even the Wei tribe has gone quiet.

37:45.149 --> 37:47.190
Life will definitely
get better day by day.

37:47.670 --> 37:48.469
The Wei tribe?

37:48.670 --> 37:49.469
Yes.

37:49.910 --> 37:51.629
The Wei tribe was in chaos years ago.

37:51.790 --> 37:55.629
Princess Lingyun, who went there
for a marital alliance, fled

37:55.989 --> 37:57.670
and returned to Cangbei
to request troops.

37:57.790 --> 37:59.949
And that finally quelled
the Wei tribe's turmoil.

38:00.109 --> 38:03.509
Since then, the Wei tribe
has been quieter year by year.

38:04.109 --> 38:05.390
Princess Lingyun?

38:06.109 --> 38:06.910
Yes.

38:08.149 --> 38:10.949
The current border markets
between Cangbei and Dachu

38:11.069 --> 38:13.310
are all thanks to Princess Lingyun.

38:13.469 --> 38:15.549
She persuaded various tribe leaders

38:15.549 --> 38:17.270
to join forces.

38:17.310 --> 38:19.190
We now have a better life.

38:19.429 --> 38:22.629
The sheep we herd
fetch even better prices than before.

38:22.750 --> 38:24.190
To commemorate her,

38:24.190 --> 38:25.589
various tribes agreed

38:25.710 --> 38:27.910
to build a statue for her.

38:27.910 --> 38:28.790
Look over there.

38:29.712 --> 38:30.288
There.

39:14.270 --> 39:16.029
Yao, come quickly.

39:20.589 --> 39:21.390
Come.

39:27.629 --> 39:30.149
Grandfather, masters,

39:30.390 --> 39:31.509
and seniors,

39:32.469 --> 39:34.429
this is Prince Ding, Mo Xiuyao.

39:34.989 --> 39:36.190
He is also my husband.

39:40.549 --> 39:41.790
Greet them.

39:46.390 --> 39:47.310
Greetings.

39:49.670 --> 39:50.469
Sit down.

39:55.109 --> 39:56.190
Don't be nervous.

39:56.710 --> 39:59.350
Grandfather and the masters
are all very good people.

40:01.830 --> 40:04.949
This is my maternal grandfather,
the headmaster of Lishan Academy.

40:06.870 --> 40:07.710
Headmaster Xu.

40:08.469 --> 40:09.549
Call him Grandfather.

40:11.549 --> 40:12.390
Grandfather.

40:18.032 --> 40:19.549
This is Master Helai.

40:19.910 --> 40:21.710
I learned all my medical skills
from him.

40:21.830 --> 40:24.509
Your legs were healed thanks to him.

40:25.870 --> 40:27.109
Thank you, Master Helai.

40:29.750 --> 40:32.432
This is Master Zhu, a sword master.

40:32.432 --> 40:33.360
I told you about him.

40:35.149 --> 40:36.109
Master Zhu.

40:38.230 --> 40:40.750
This is Master Chen,
a first-rate mathematician.

40:41.830 --> 40:43.670
He wrote the Essentials of Mathematics.

40:45.509 --> 40:46.350
Master Chen.

40:47.989 --> 40:50.149
And they're Master Yu and Master Jiang.

40:51.190 --> 40:53.109
Master Yu, Master Jiang.

41:02.429 --> 41:04.750
Grandfather, masters,

41:05.149 --> 41:06.310
and seniors,

41:07.310 --> 41:09.808
before I left the mountain,
you always worried,

41:10.429 --> 41:12.629
afraid I couldn't adapt
to life down the mountain

41:13.469 --> 41:16.304
and that I would be bullied
after marrying Prince Ding.

41:17.509 --> 41:20.549
Now that you've met Yao,
you should be relieved.

41:22.109 --> 41:23.190
He treats me very well.

41:23.670 --> 41:26.390
He always patiently listens
to every word I say

41:26.830 --> 41:27.910
and is considerate of me.

41:29.029 --> 41:30.350
I am living very well.

41:44.270 --> 41:45.109
Grandfather,

41:47.350 --> 41:48.270
masters,

41:49.989 --> 41:52.989
and all seniors of Lishan Academy,

41:54.029 --> 41:57.390
I am Mo Xiuyao, Li's husband.

41:59.069 --> 41:59.989
Thank you all.

42:01.750 --> 42:03.109
I will be good to Li.

42:05.429 --> 42:07.029
I will cherish her with my life.

42:11.870 --> 42:13.190
Thank you for your care of her.

42:14.870 --> 42:15.670
From now on,

42:17.390 --> 42:19.589
I won't let her be all alone anymore.

42:22.149 --> 42:23.390
You can rest assured.

42:44.496 --> 42:47.472
(Preview)

42:47.670 --> 42:49.350
We're running out of time.
Open the door!

42:49.429 --> 42:50.230
Li,

42:50.469 --> 42:53.109
if we leave the mountain
to seek help now,

42:53.190 --> 42:54.710
it'd be bowing to the rebels.

42:54.710 --> 42:57.509
Was Su Zuidie executed
after being taken back to Cangbei?

42:57.549 --> 42:59.989
She probably died quite miserably.

43:00.190 --> 43:02.270
I appoint you
as the Secret Investigator of Lishan.

43:02.390 --> 43:04.549
(Lishan Academy)
Go to Lishan and find out the truth.

43:04.750 --> 43:07.790
If everyone is dead,
what use is an empty reputation?

43:15.097 --> 43:21.689
♪Memories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreams♪

43:25.273 --> 43:31.417
♪Only by moving forward
can you find reunion♪

43:33.625 --> 43:36.857
♪Endings only mark new routes♪

43:37.081 --> 43:43.097
♪It's all part of the scenery♪

43:43.417 --> 43:46.841
♪To the horizon's call♪

43:46.905 --> 43:53.465
♪Your journey hasn't started♪

43:54.521 --> 43:58.457
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

43:58.457 --> 44:04.153
♪Both joy and grief
make the trip worthwhile♪

44:04.665 --> 44:13.273
♪Trying to catch up
to your own lost shadow♪

44:14.169 --> 44:19.673
♪Within the wilds, echoes thrive♪

44:19.673 --> 44:25.177
♪Clear mind leads to a clear path♪

44:25.241 --> 44:29.305
♪Be grateful to your losses♪

44:29.593 --> 44:34.817
♪Make your steps weightless♪

44:35.417 --> 44:39.129
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

44:39.161 --> 44:44.825
♪Let time embrace you
and wash away the past♪

44:45.593 --> 44:53.561
♪Put every twist behind you,
drift leisurely through time♪

44:54.969 --> 45:00.217
♪Make headway against the wind,
let mountains bow to your pace♪

45:00.473 --> 45:06.377
♪Rush towards a life without regret♪

45:06.377 --> 45:10.497
♪Let your nature burst free♪

45:10.713 --> 45:15.449
♪Unbound by form♪

45:16.665 --> 45:20.937
♪Let your nature burst free♪

45:21.177 --> 45:26.617
♪Unbound by form♪
